DynamoRIO API

Packages Available for Download

Official DynamoRIO packages are hosted as GitHub releases. For more recent bug fixes and features prior to the next official release, [weekly builds are available](Latest-Build) for recent commits.

Direct Download Links

For the very latest changes since the last official release, you can download a [weekly build](Latest-Build).

The 8.0.0 release:

  • DynamoRIO-Windows-8.0.0-1.zip
  • DynamoRIO-Linux-8.0.0-1.tar.gz
  • DynamoRIO-ARM-Linux-EABIHF-8.0.0-1.tar.gz
  • DynamoRIO-ARM-Android-EABI-8.0.0-1.tar.gz
  • DynamoRIO-AArch64-Linux-8.0.0-1.tar.gz

Please note that older releases than 8.0.0 do not support recent operating systems, in particular recent Windows versions from Windows 10 1809 onward.
